                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does the right hon. Gentleman think it reasonable to spend £100 this year where we spent £9 before the war, on publicity?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bfbf8c88-bf46-48bb-b48b-b02a33909925" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-10-17/debates/72257f8e-8813-473d-a234-b81ebc3baa54/CentralOfficeOfInformation#contribution-bfbf8c88-bf46-48bb-b48b-b02a33909925">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
